The paper proposes a load clustering method using robust principal component analysis and submodular optimization. This involves machine learning techniques and optimization algorithms, which are commonly associated with the sub-categories of cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks). The paper also deals with load analysis and modeling, which are relevant to the sub-categories of cs.SY (Systems and Control) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
